title: Ejipuri!
description: Ko is a handsome high school boy who normally can't stand girls, but he falls head over heels for Cleo, a genuine modern-day mural-girl who walks like an Egyptian! A blast from the past 5000 years in the making, it's the Egypti-est romantic comedy around!
author: Naoda Tsuboko

1.title: Something's Wrong With My Best Friend
